OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FJohn Lewis planning major  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fworkforce cuts             
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, John Lewis has confirmed it is planning
OL,6, to further cut its workforce over the  
OL,7, next five years.                       
OL,9,FUp to 11,000 jobs at the retail        
OL,10,Fpartnership - amounting to 10% of the  
OL,11,Fworkforce - could reportedly go,       
OL,12,Faccording to the Guardian.             
OL,14,FJohn Lewis said the losses would       
OL,15,Finclude redundancies and not replacing 
OL,16,Fvacant positions.                      
OL,18,FIt would not confirm numbers to the    
OL,19,FBBC, but said plans to return the      
OL,20,Fbusiness to profit would mean cuts.    
